"fib.mst — sprint_s06_detail.md 'Benchmarks'. Reopens Integer under its
 TRUE superclass Number (Pitfall P2 — Integer's actual genesis superclass,
 not Object). Not in world.list; `macvm run world/bench/fib.mst --world
 world` loads it explicitly."

Number subclass: Integer [
    fib [
        self < 2 ifTrue: [ ^self ].
        ^(self - 1) fib + (self - 2) fib
    ]
]

Transcript show: 25 fib printString.
Transcript cr.
